  }, "v18"), mdx("p", null, "Ngo\xE0i ra c\u0169ng mang theo m\u01B0\u1EDDi mi\u1EBFng ph\xF3 m\xE1t cho vi\xEAn ch\u1EC9 huy v\xE0 cho c\xE1c anh con. Xem th\u1EED c\xE1c anh con ra sao r\u1ED3i mang v\u1EC1 cho cha b\u1EB1ng c\u1EDB g\xEC \u0111\u1EC3 th\u1EA5y ch\xFAng n\xF3 b\xECnh y\xEAn. "), mdx("h6", {
